mplementation into phases/steps -->\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ## 9. Future Changes\n66: \n67: <!-- TODO: List known future changes, limitations, and technical debt -->\n\n(End of file - total 67 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the purpose and role of the CLI pack command -->\n\n### 1.2 Package Layout\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the directory and package structure -->\n\n### 1.3 Data Flow\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the data flow and component interactions -->\n\n### 1.4 Dependencies\n\n<!-- TODO: List direct dependencies and their purposes -->\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/design.md","time":{"start":1775851803832,"end":1775851803840}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775851805142,"sessionID":"ses_286fc20dbffego1zy9g3xNGXzV","part":{"id":"prt_d79041549001CSHj2CtrrJhd9q","messageID":"msg_d7903f7d60018RrwDu27NEJc0H","sessionID":"ses_286fc20dbffego1zy9g3xNGXzV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_b6b42e45e5b9480db4be6807","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-020/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-020/design.md`, `changes/AR-020/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 创建 Python CLI 项目脚手架\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/` 目录\n12: - [ ] 1.2 创建 `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`，包含：\n13:   - `name = \"agentcube\"`, `requires-python = \">=3.10\"`, `version = \"0.1.0\"`\n14:   - `[project] dependencies`: typer[all]>=0.9.0, pydantic>=2.0.0, pyyaml>=6.0, httpx>=0.24.0, docker>=6.0.0, rich>=13.0.0, packaging>=23.0, importlib-resources>=6.0.0, semver>=3.0.0\n15:   - `[project.optional-dependencies]`: k8s, dev, test（与 cli-toolkit/design.md 依赖表一致）\n16:   - `[project.scripts]`: `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n17:   - `[tool.setuptools] packages`: agentcube, agentcube.cli, agentcube.runtime, agentcube.operations, agentcube.services\n18:   - `[tool.pytest.ini_options]`: testpaths = [\"tests\"]\n19:   - `[tool.ruff]`, `[tool.mypy]` 基础配置\n20: - [ ] 1.3 创建包目录结构：\n21:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py`（`__version__ = \"0.1.0\"`, `__author__`, `__email__`, 导出占位）\n22:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n23:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n24:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n25:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n26:   - `cmd/cli/agentcube/operations/__init__.py`\n27:   - `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py`\n28: - [ ] 1.4 创建 `.gitignore`（`__pycache__/`, `*.pyc`, `.pytest_cache/`, `dist/`, `build/`, `*.egg-info/`）\n29: - [ ] 1.5 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n30: - [ ] 1.6 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 和 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认工具链可用\n31: \n32: **Verification:** `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` exit 0；`python -c \"import agentcube; print(agentcube.__version__)\"` 输出 `0.1.0`；ruff 和 mypy 无致命错误\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## T2. 实现 MetadataOptions 数据类 — agentcube/models/pack_models.py\n37: \n38: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n39: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `MetadataOptions` dataclass，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §MetadataOptions 表一致：\n40:   `agent_name: Optional[str] = None`\n41:   `language: Optional[str] = \"python\"`\n42:   `entrypoint: Optional[str] = None`\n43:   `port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n44:   `build_mode: Optional[str] = \"local\"`\n45:   `requirements_file: Optional[str] = None`\n46:   `description: Optional[str] = None`\n47:   `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n48:   `router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n49:   `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n50:   `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080`\n51:   `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n52:   `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n53:   `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n54:   `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n55: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `@classmethod from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\"` 类方法：\n56:   - 从 options dict 中提取已知字段，忽略未知字段\n57:   - 返回 `MetadataOptions` 实例\n58: - [ ] 2.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py`\n59: - [ ] 2.5 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_Defaults`：无参构造 → 所有字段为默认值\n60: - [ ] 2.6 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Full`：完整 options dict → 字段完全匹配\n61: - [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_Partial`：部分 options dict → 缺失字段为默认值\n62: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestMetadataOptions_FromOptions_UnknownFields`：含未知字段 → 忽略未知字段，已知字段正确\n63: \n64: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py -v` 全部通过\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## T3. 实现 AgentMetadata Pydantic 模型 — agentcube/services/metadata_service.py（部分）\n69: \n70: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n71: - [ ] 3.2 定义 `AgentMetadata(BaseModel)`，字段与 cli-toolkit/design.md §AgentMetadata 表一致：\n72:   `agent_name: str`（required）\n73:   `description: Optional[str] = None`\n74:   `language: str = \"python\"`\n75:   `entrypoint: str`（required）\n76:   `port: int = 8080`\n77:   `build_mode: str = \"local\"`\n78:   `region: Optional[str] = None`\n79:   `version: Optional[str] = None`\n80:   `image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n81:   `auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n82:   `requirements_file: Optional[str] = \"requirements.txt\"`\n83:   `registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n84:   `registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n85:   `registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"`\n86:   `agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = None`\n87:   `workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None`\n88:   `router_url: Optional[str] = None`\n89:   `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None`\n90:   `readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None`\n91:   `agent_id: Optional[str] = None`\n92:   `session_id: Optional[str] = None`\n93:   `k8s_deployment: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None`\n94: - [ ] 3.3 实现 Pydantic v2 validators（`@field_validator`）：\n95:   - `validate_language`: 限制为 `['python', 'java']`，转小写\n96:   - `validate_build_mode`: 限制为 `['local', 'cloud']`，转小写\n97:   - `validate_port`: 范围 1–65535\n98: - [ ] 3.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py`\n99: - [ ] 3.5 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidCreation`：合法字段 → 模型创建成功\n100: - [ ] 3.6 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Python`：`language=\"Python\"` → 规范化为 `\"python\"`\n101: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Java`：`language=\"java\"` → 通过\n102: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateLanguage_Rejected`：`language=\"nodejs\"` → `ValidationError`\n103: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Local`：`build_mode=\"local\"` → 通过\n104: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Cloud`：`build_mode=\"cloud\"` → 通过\n105: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidateBuildMode_Rejected`：`build_mode=\"hybrid\"` → `ValidationError`\n106: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Valid`：`port=8080` → 通过\n107: - [ ] 3.13 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Zero`：`port=0` → `ValidationError`\n108: - [ ] 3.14 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ValidatePort_Overflow`：`port=70000` → `ValidationError`\n109: - [ ] 3.15 测试 `TestAgentMetadata_ModelDump`：`model_dump(exclude_none=True)` 不包含 None 字段\n110: \n111: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Port validation 和 §Build mode validation 和 §Language validation 全部场景\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## T4. 实现 MetadataService — YAML 加载/保存与回退链\n116: \n117: - [ ] 4.1 在 `metadata_service.py` 中定义 `MetadataService` 类：\n118:   - `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n119: - [ ] 4.2 实现 `load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata`：\n120:   - 按回退链尝试加载：`agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`\n121:   - 使用 `yaml.safe_load()` 解析 YAML\n122:   - 将 dict 传入 `AgentMetadata(**data)` 构造模型\n123:   - 三个文件都不存在时返回 `None`\n124: - [ ] 4.3 实现 `save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n125:   - 使用 `yaml.dump(metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True), default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False)`\n126:   - 写入 `{workspace_path}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n127: - [ ] 4.4 实现 `update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n128:   - 先调用 `load_metadata` 加载现有元数据\n129:   - 如不存在则创建默认 `AgentMetadata`\n130:   - 合并 updates dict 到现有模型（使用 `model_copy(update=updates)` 或等价方式）\n131:   - 调用 `save_metadata` 保存\n132:   - 返回更新后的 `AgentMetadata`\n133: - [ ] 4.5 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py`\n134: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_PrimaryExists`：`agent_metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n135: - [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_FirstFallback`：仅 `agent.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n136: - [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_SecondFallback`：仅 `metadata.yaml` 存在 → 正确加载\n137: - [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestLoadMetadata_NoneExist`：三个文件都不存在 → 返回 `None`\n138: - [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_RoundTrip`：保存后重新加载 → 数据一致\n139: - [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_ExcludeNone`：保存的 YAML 不包含 null 值\n140: - [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestSaveMetadata_Format`：YAML 使用 `default_flow_style=False, indent=2, sort_keys=False`\n141: - [ ] 4.13 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_Merge`：部分更新 → 未更新字段保留原值\n142: - [ ] 4.14 测试 `TestUpdateMetadata_CreateNew`：无现有文件 → 创建新元数据\n143: \n144: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Metadata loading with fallback chain 全部 4 个场景\n145: \n146: ---\n147: \n148: ## T5. 实现工作区验证 — PackRuntime._validate_workspace_structure\n149: \n150: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n151: - [ ] 5.2 定义 `PackRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)`\n152: - [ ] 5.3 实现 `_validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n153:   - 路径不存在 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path does not exist: {workspace_path}\")`\n154:   - 路径不是目录 → `ValueError(f\"Workspace path is not a directory: {workspace_path}\")`\n155: - [ ] 5.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py`\n156: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_ValidDirectory`：有效目录 → 无异常\n157: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_NotExists`：路径不存在 → `ValueError`\n158: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_IsFile`：路径是文件而非目录 → `ValueError`\n159: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestValidateWorkspace_SymlinkToDirectory`：符号链接指向目录 → 通过\n160: \n161: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_workspace.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Workspace validation — not a directory 场景\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## T6. 实现元数据加载与创建 — PackRuntime._load_or_create_metadata\n166: \n167: - [ ] 6.1 实现 `_load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n168:   - 调用 `self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)` 尝试加载\n169:   - 如返回 None，从 options 构造 `MetadataOptions`，再用默认值创建新 `AgentMetadata`\n170:   - 新元数据的 `agent_name` 从 workspace 目录名推断（如 options 中未提供）\n171: - [ ] 6.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_metadata_load.py`\n172: - [ ] 6.3 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_ExistingFile`：存在 `agent_metadata.yaml` → 加载并返回\n173: - [ ] 6.4 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_FallbackChain`：仅 `agent.yaml` 存在 → 通过回退链加载\n174: - [ ] 6.5 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_FromOptions`：无文件，有 options → 从 options 创建\n175: - [ ] 6.6 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_InferName`：无文件无 agent_name → 从目录名推断\n176: - [ ] 6.7 测试 `TestLoadOrCreateMetadata_CreateNew_Defaults`：无文件无 options → 使用全部默认值\n177: \n178: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_metadata_load.py -v` 全部通过\n179: \n180: ---\n181: \n182: ## T7. 实现选项合并 — PackRuntime._apply_option_overrides\n183: \n184: - [ ] 7.1 实现 `_apply_option_overrides(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata`：\n185:   - 遍历 CLI 覆盖选项：`agent_name`, `language`, `entrypoint`, `port`, `build_mode`, `description`\n186:   - 仅当选项值非 None 时覆盖 metadata 对应字段\n187:   - 使用 `metadata.model_copy(update=updates)` 创建新实例（触发 Pydantic validators）\n188:   - 返回更新后的 `AgentMetadata`\n189: - [ ] 7.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_overrides.py`\n190: - [ ] 7.3 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_AgentName`：`--agent-name \"new-agent\"` → `metadata.agent_name` 更新\n191: - [ ] 7.4 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_Language`：`--language \"java\"` → `metadata.language` 更新并触发 validator\n192: - [ ] 7.5 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_Entrypoint`：`--entrypoint \"python app.py\"` → 更新\n193: - [ ] 7.6 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_Port`：`--port 9090` → 更新\n194: - [ ] 7.7 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_BuildMode`：`--build-mode \"cloud\"` → 更新\n195: - [ ] 7.8 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_Description`：`--description \"new desc\"` → 更新\n196: - [ ] 7.9 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_NonePreserved`：选项为 None → 原 metadata 值保留\n197: - [ ] 7.10 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_Multiple`：同时覆盖多个字段 → 全部更新\n198: - [ ] 7.11 测试 `TestApplyOverrides_InvalidLanguage`：`--language \"nodejs\"` → `ValidationError`\n199: \n200: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_overrides.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Metadata merge — CLI overrides 全部 7 个场景\n201: \n202: ---\n203: \n204: ## T8. 实现入口点推断 — PackRuntime._infer_entrypoint\n205: \n206: - [ ] 8.1 实现 `_infer_entrypoint(self, workspace_path: Path, language: str) -> str`：\n207:   - Python 语言：\n208:     - 查找 `main.py` → 返回 `\"python main.py\"`\n209:     - 否则查找第一个 `.py` 文件 → 返回 `\"python <filename>\"`\n210:     - 无 `.py` 文件 → `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace. Provide --entrypoint explicitly.\")`\n211:   - Java 语言：\n212:     - 尝试解析 `pom.xml` 中的 `mainClass` → 返回 `\"java -jar target/<artifact>.jar\"`\n213:     - 无法解析 → 返回 `\"java -jar target/*.jar\"`\n214:   - 不支持的语言 → `ValueError(f\"Cannot infer entrypoint for language: {language}\")`\n215: - [ ] 8.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_entrypoint.py`\n216: - [ ] 8.3 测试 `TestInferEntrypoint_Python_MainPy`：存在 `main.py` → `\"python main.py\"`\n217: - [ ] 8.4 测试 `TestInferEntrypoint_Python_AlternativePy`：仅存在 `app.py` → `\"python app.py\"`\n218: - [ ] 8.5 测试 `TestInferEntrypoint_Python_NoPyFiles`：无 `.py` 文件 → `ValueError`\n219: - [ ] 8.6 测试 `TestInferEntrypoint_Java_Default`：Java 语言无 pom.xml 解析 → `\"java -jar target/*.jar\"`\n220: - [ ] 8.7 测试 `TestInferEntrypoint_UnsupportedLanguage`：`language=\"nodejs\"` → `ValueError`\n221: \n222: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_entrypoint.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Entrypoint inference 全部场景\n223: \n224: ---\n225: \n226: ## T9. 实现语言兼容性验证 — Python 和 Java\n227: \n228: - [ ] 9.1 实现 `_validate_language_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n229:   - 根据 `metadata.language` 分发到 `_validate_python_compatibility` 或 `_validate_java_compatibility`\n230: - [ ] 9.2 实现 `_validate_python_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n231:   - 检查至少一个 `*.py` 文件存在 → 无则 `ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")`\n232:   - 如 `requirements_file` 指定，检查该文件存在 → 无则 `ValueError(f\"Dependency file not found: {requirements_file}\")`\n233: - [ ] 9.3 实现 `_validate_java_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n234:   - 检查 `pom.xml` 存在 → 无则 `ValueError(\"pom.xml is required for Java projects\")`\n235:   - 验证 `pom.xml` 为有效 XML（`xml.etree.ElementTree.parse`）→ 无效则 `ValueError(\"Invalid pom.xml: not valid XML\")`\n236: - [ ] 9.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_validation.py`\n237: - [ ] 9.5 测试 `TestValidateLanguageCompatibility_Python`：Python 语言 → 调用 `_validate_python_compatibility`\n238: - [ ] 9.6 测试 `TestValidateLanguageCompatibility_Java`：Java 语言 → 调用 `_validate_java_compatibility`\n239: - [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestValidatePython_HasPyFiles`：有 `.py` 文件 → 通过\n240: - [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestValidatePython_NoPyFiles`：无 `.py` 文件 → `ValueError`\n241: - [ ] 9.9 测试 `TestValidatePython_MissingRequirements`：指定 requirements_file 不存在 → `ValueError`\n242: - [ ] 9.10 测试 `TestValidatePython_CustomRequirements`：自定义 requirements_file 存在 → 通过\n243: - [ ] 9.11 测试 `TestValidateJava_HasPomXml`：有效 `pom.xml` → 通过\n244: - [ ] 9.12 测试 `TestValidateJava_NoPomXml`：无 `pom.xml` → `ValueError`\n245: - [ ] 9.13 测试 `TestValidateJava_InvalidPomXml`：`pom.xml` 非有效 XML → `ValueError`\n246: \n247: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_validation.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Python compatibility validation 和 §Java compatibility validation 和 §Workspace validation — Java-specific 全部场景\n248: \n249: ---\n250: \n251: ## T10. 实现依赖处理 — PackRuntime._process_dependencies\n252: \n253: - [ ] 10.1 实现 `_process_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n254:   - 根据 `metadata.language` 分发到 `_process_python_dependencies` 或 `_process_java_dependencies`\n255: - [ ] 10.2 实现 `_process_python_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n256:   - 读取 `requirements_file`（默认 `requirements.txt`）\n257:   - 验证文件格式（非空行应为有效 pip 依赖格式）\n258:   - 文件不存在时静默跳过（已在 T9 验证阶段检查）\n259: - [ ] 10.3 实现 `_process_java_dependencies(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None`：\n260:   - 解析 `pom.xml` 提取依赖信息（仅作验证，不修改）\n261:   - 验证 `pom.xml` 包含 `<dependencies>` 节点（可选，仅记录 warning）\n262: - [ ] 10.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dependencies.py`\n263: - [ ] 10.5 测试 `TestProcessDependencies_Python`：Python 语言 → 调用 `_process_python_dependencies`\n264: - [ ] 10.6 测试 `TestProcessDependencies_Java`：Java 语言 → 调用 `_process_java_dependencies`\n265: - [ ] 10.7 测试 `TestProcessPythonDependencies_ValidRequirements`：有效 `requirements.txt` → 通过\n266: - [ ] 10.8 测试 `TestProcessPythonDependencies_CustomFile`：自定义 requirements_file → 读取正确文件\n267: - [ ] 10.9 测试 `TestProcessJavaDependencies_ValidPom`：有效 `pom.xml` → 通过\n268: - [ ] 10.10 测试 `TestProcessJavaDependencies_NoDependencies`：`pom.xml` 无 `<dependencies>` → 通过（仅 warning）\n269: \n270: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dependencies.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Dependency processing 全部场景\n271: \n272: ---\n273: \n274: ## T11. 实现 Python Dockerfile 生成 — PackRuntime._generate_python_dockerfile\n275: \n276: - [ ] 11.1 实现 `_generate_python_dockerfile(self, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> str`：\n277:   - 生成 Dockerfile 内容，包含：\n278:     - `FROM python:3.10-slim`\n279:     - `WORKDIR /app`\n280:     - `COPY {requirements_file} .`（或 `requirements.txt`）\n281:     - `RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r {requirements_file}`\n282:     - `COPY . .`\n283:     - `EXPOSE {metadata.port}`\n284:     - `CMD [\"{entrypoint_parts...}\"]`（entrypoint 按空格分割为 JSON array）\n285:   - 返回 Dockerfile 内容字符串\n286: - [ ] 11.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_dockerfile_python.py`\n287: - [ ] 11.3 测试 `TestGeneratePythonDockerfile_BaseImage`：包含 `FROM python:3.